{
  "stem": "4113.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And when I visited in Australia a few years ago, she was telling me an incident where she and another girl-- a Polish girl who worked with her-- were called in by the officer in charge of the officer's club.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he screamed and yelled at them that they supposedly were stealing food and taking it with them to the barracks.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And another soldier stood there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He apparently was the accuser, that he caught them doing it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she said the following-- and he said if he catches them again, he's going to deliver them to the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The following day that same officer calls them in again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he says, look, what I told you yesterday, forget.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Take as much food as you want.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she was telling me that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It is just to give you an idea that, you know, it depends what you were exposed to, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you speak, most Jews were exposed to the SS all the time, you see.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Whereas I was also exposed to the Wehrmacht and to the Luftwaffe where you saw decent people, you see?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So, anyway, we were there in 1943.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Around February of 1943, you may remember, the Germans suffered their first defeat at Stalingrad.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was a bad time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was the uprising starting in-- in Warsaw, you see.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my brother was still in that town, Jaslo, cleaning up from the ghetto there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was glazing there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He worked there as a glazier.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was also glazing in jail.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's how we found out that two girls from my hometown tried to escape from a little camp in Trzebinia-- which was a village between our town and Jaslo-- with two Ukrainian guardsmen who fell in love with them.",
      "word_count": 39
    }
  ],
